message: If you insist on making expungement laws nugatory and prejudicing already-acquitted persons, kindly take it to the talk page. Please note that the 'personal life' section is a recent addition; thus, the status quo was without it. It therefore falls upon those who wish to change said status quo to take it to the talk page and prove why its mention is necessary. Undid revision 937624385 by [[Special:Contributions/Lullabying|Lullabying]] ([[User talk:Lullabying|talk]])

Violative of expungement law and in derogation of clean-slate policy. As defendant was acquitted and the records officially expunged, putting the unsubstantiated and false charge against him in his profile to mark him for life borders maliciousness and should not be condoned. Please stop putting information that unnecessarily promote discrimination against those falsely accused.
